---
export const prerender = false;
import HiddenGrammarLayout from '../../../layouts/HiddenGrammarLayout.astro';
---

<HiddenGrammarLayout title="Hidden Grammar Deck — Art Lab">
  <div class="deck-page">

    <!-- ── BREADCRUMB ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <nav class="hg-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/hidden-grammar">Art Lab</a>
      <span class="hg-breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
      <a href="/hidden-grammar/toolkit">Toolkit</a>
      <span class="hg-breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
      <span>Hidden Grammar Deck</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- ── HEADER ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <header class="deck-header">
      <div class="deck-header-meta">
        <span class="badge badge--demo">Demo</span>
        <span class="deck-phase">· Framework Reference</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="deck-title">Hidden Grammar Deck</h1>
      <p class="deck-tagline">11 Roots. 54 Principles. Nine slides. A visual introduction to the framework behind every Art Lab tool.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- ── EMBED ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="deck-embed-wrap">
      <iframe
        src="https://claude.site/artifacts/882c82eb-3faf-4d6d-b7ae-1e265104a6ff/embed"
        title="Hidden Grammar Deck"
        width="100%"
        height="600"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="clipboard-write"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <p class="deck-nav-hint">Navigate with arrow keys, spacebar, or click the dots at the bottom of the deck.</p>

    <!-- ── ABOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="deck-about">
      <h2 class="deck-about-title">What this is</h2>
      <p>The Hidden Grammar Deck is a standalone artifact that walks through the framework underlying Art Lab — the 11 Roots, the 54 Principles, and how they function as a shared vocabulary for talking about what's actually happening in a work of art.</p>
      <p>The framing is this: the framework is a type system, not a prompt. Domain confusion is a type error. The RAP Protocol is a proof requirement. If you've analyzed a piece with Art Lab and gotten results that surprised you, this deck explains why the framework produces those results — and what it's actually checking for.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ── BOTTOM NAV ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="deck-bottom-nav">
      <a href="/hidden-grammar/toolkit" class="hg-btn hg-btn--ghost">
        ← All tools
      </a>
      <a href="/hidden-grammar/framework" class="hg-btn hg-btn--ghost">
        Full framework reference →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</HiddenGrammarLayout>

<style>
  .deck-page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .deck-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .deck-header-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .badge--demo {
    background: #ede9fe;
    color: #5b21b6;
  }

  .deck-phase {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  .deck-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .deck-tagline {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Embed ── */
  .deck-embed-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0;
    background: #000;
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .deck-embed-wrap iframe {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 600px;
  }

  .deck-nav-hint {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ── About ── */
  .deck-about {
    border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .deck-about-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #4f46e5;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
  }

  .deck-about p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .deck-about p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Bottom nav ── */
  .deck-bottom-nav {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .deck-title { font-size: 1.625rem; }
    .deck-embed-wrap iframe { height: 480px; }
    .deck-bottom-nav { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
